title: Aquila Court Apts- Spacious 2 BR Available. SAVE MONEY, RENT SPECIAL!
posting_body: ['***RENT SPECIAL: APPLY THE SAME DAY AS YOUR SHOWING & GET A $500 RENT CREDIT!', '*** CALL TODAY FOR MORE DETAILS', '*Prices and availability are subject to change at any time.', 'Aquila Court offers 2 bedroom apartment homes in Saint Louis Park, MN.', ' Variety of finishes-', 'CLASSIC, OAK & CHERRY CABINETRY.', 'Minutes from shopping, Knollwood Mall, dining, recreation, entertainment and much more!', ' Convenient to Downtown Minneapolis.', 'AVAILABLE NOW', 'Starting at $1,250/month', 'Lease Terms: Month-to-Month rental agreement with a 9 month clause.', '$40 application fee per adult.', 'PETS WELCOME- Cats, Birds and Fish', 'Cats accepted with the following restrictions:', 'Cats - $250 non-refundable pet fee, $30 monthly pet rent, a limit of 2 cats per unit, and must be spayed/neutered.', 'Utilities: We pay for your heat, water, sewer, and trash pick-up.', 'Resident is  responsible for', 'electricity, cable and internet.', 'Call today and let our professional staff give you a personal tour of the community.', 'show contact info', 'Check out all our other apartment communities at <URL>', '*Prices are subject to change at anytime.']
